{"Id":871132,"Title":"浣溪沙四首","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"刘永平","Context":"动后初传夺虏旗。山遥水阔雁来迟。平安为报岭梅知。洛水非遥频击梦，锦城堪恋未忘归。停骖返旆乍沉思。细雨秋风卧剑南。野溪初涨近茅庵。满天愁雾暗垂帘。去国仓皇魂梦苦，停云检点泪痕添。雁零鸿断我何堪。榻冷初惊落叶霜。江楼月黑夜茫茫。青灯一豆照回廊。寻梦难成终有恨，耽吟不寐亦何妨。麝尘莲寸此情长。月照绯帷透暗香。兰灯静照寂寒窗。几声更鼓入苔墙。被借笼薰方觉暖，宵因客久始知长。吟梅小院意难忘。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"浣溪沙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"89f2d8197422082d06f1fd71f8865e67","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5234210,"Sentence":"动后初传夺虏旗。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dòng hòu chū chuán duó lǔ qǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234211,"Sentence":"山遥水阔雁来迟。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shān yáo shui kuò yàn lái chǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234212,"Sentence":"平安为报岭梅知。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"pǐng ān wéi bào ling méi zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234213,"Sentence":"洛水非遥频击梦，锦城堪恋未忘归。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"luò shui fēi yáo pǐn jī mèng ，jin chéng kān liàn wèi wàng guī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234214,"Sentence":"停骖返旆乍沉思。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tǐng cān fǎn pèi zhà chén sāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234215,"Sentence":"细雨秋风卧剑南。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xì yǔ qīu fēng wò jiàn nā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234216,"Sentence":"野溪初涨近茅庵。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yě xī chū zhǎng jìn máo ān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234217,"Sentence":"满天愁雾暗垂帘。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mǎn tiān chóu wù àn chuǐ lián ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5234218,"Sentence":"去国仓皇魂梦苦，停云检点泪痕添。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qù guó cāng huáng hún mèng kǔ ，tǐng yún jiǎn diǎn lèi hén tiān ","Tag":null,"